Define an explicit capabilities/constraints matrix for Planner, Coder, and the human user (in both planner and coder sessions): what each actor must be able to do, and what each actor must be prevented from doing, with respect to $PLANROOT (plan structure, descriptions, status updates, current_objective) and $REPOROOT (code changes). The result should be precise enough to drive AGENTS.md wording and to evaluate whether a proposed access-control design actually enforces the intended behavior.
